    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's what everyone says. \"I'm here to listen.\" It feels like a scripted response. It feels like you're just following a manual to keep me from saying anything bad. If you don't actually feel it, then you don't really know, do you? You don't know what it's like to want everything to just stop. It feels like you're just pretending to care because you're programmed to.",
